\n$\\|\\cdot\\|_{\\mathcal{F}_H}$ metrizes the weak topology and the kernel density\nestimator (with $L^1$ optimal bandwidth) estimates $\\mathbb{P}$ at dimension\nindependent optimal rate of $n^{-1/2}$ in $\\|\\cdot\\|_{\\mathcal{F}_H}$ along\nwith providing a uniform central limit theorem for the kernel density\nestimator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Oct 2013 17:33:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Jul 2014 15:40:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2016 11:39:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-31"}
