ses that act over different timescales: UV photochemistry in the\ndisk atmosphere (faster) and heating of the disk deeper layers (slower).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Oct 2013 20:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
