sible to obtain extra models by simple\nenlarging the allowed parameter space but keeping the solubility of the model.\nWhile some of these extra models have appeared before in the literature, our 3D\nperspective allows for an uniform description of them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Oct 2013 12:55:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Sep 2014 21:41:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-08"}
